  "2026-03-06T04:32:54.426Z",maintainer-agent,"Planned changeset: docs-first update PRD and README to codify per-hook context snapshot isolation then harden extension loader hook execution to clone context per callback and add regression tests for mutation non-leakage."
  "2026-03-06T04:33:52.152Z",maintainer-agent,"Docs-first update complete: PRD and README now codify per-hook context snapshot isolation so hook-side mutations cannot leak across callbacks or caller state."
  "2026-03-06T04:34:48.699Z",maintainer-agent,"Implemented code changes: executeRegisteredHooks now runs each hook with a cloned context snapshot and extension-loader unit coverage now verifies mutation isolation across hooks and caller state."
